### Test Database Connection
GET http://localhost:5160/test-db
Accept: application/json

###

### Create Account via Controller
POST http://localhost:5160/api/account
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "policyNumber": "POL-CTRL-001",
  "policyAccountNumber": "ACC-CTRL-001",
  "balance": 5000.00
}

###

### Create Another Account via Controller
POST http://localhost:5160/api/account
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "policyNumber": "POL-CTRL-002",
  "policyAccountNumber": "ACC-CTRL-002", 
  "balance": 7500.25
}

###

### Get Account by Policy Number
GET http://localhost:5160/api/account/POL-CTRL-001
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Account by Policy Number (Not Found)
GET http://localhost:5160/api/account/POL-CTRL-999
Accept: application/json

